## AI Core Contract

1. Prioritize reusing existing UI components in the project; do not reinvent the wheel
2. Reference colors and spacing only via Design Tokens / CSS variables / Tailwind semantic classes
3. Review existing components and patterns in the project before modifying UI
4. Do not introduce third-party UI libraries whose style is inconsistent with the project's existing design system
